---
---
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>MORPHOS | AI-Powered Parametric CAD for CNC & 3D Printing</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-950 text-white font-sans selection:bg-blue-500/30">
		<nav class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-b border-white/5">
			<div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-blue-500">MORPHOS</div>
			<div class="flex items-center gap-8">
				<a href="#features" class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest">Features</a>
				<a href="/app" class="bg-blue-600 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm hover:bg-blue-500 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-blue-600/20 active:scale-95">Launch App</a>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-24 relative">
			{/* Decorative elements */}
			<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[500px] bg-blue-600/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full -z-10"></div>

			<section class="text-center space-y-12 mb-32">
				<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600/10 border border-blue-600/20 rounded-full text-blue-400 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] animate-pulse">
					Now with Replicad & Makerjs Support
				</div>
				<h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-white to-slate-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
					Design anything <br /> with AI precision.
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
					Generate professional **2D paths** for CNC and **3D models** for printing from natural language. Parametric, editable, and industry-standard.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6 pt-4">
					<a href="/app" class="bg-white text-black px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-slate-200 transition-all shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">
						Get Started Now
					</a>
					<a href="#demo" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all border border-slate-800 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">
						Watch Demo
					</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="features" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 py-24 border-t border-white/5">
				<div class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-[32px] border border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">🧊</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">Parametric 3D</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed">Advanced mechanical parts powered by Replicad. Export high-fidelity **STEP** and **STL** files ready for production.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-[32px] border border-white/5 hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">📐</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">CNC Ready 2D</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed">Precise vector paths with Makerjs. Generate **SVG** and **DXF** for laser cutters, plasma, and CNC routers.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-[32px] border border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-600/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">📷</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">Image-to-CAD</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed">Upload a hand-drawn sketch or a photo. Our AI analyzes dimensions and converts it into editable CAD code instantly.</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="py-24 text-center">
				<div class="bg-blue-600 rounded-[48px] p-16 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-600/20">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-white/20 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8 relative z-10">Ready to build the future?</h2>
					<p class="text-blue-100 text-lg font-medium mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto relative z-10 opacity-90">Join thousands of engineers and makers using MORPHOS to speed up their design-to-production workflow.</p>
					<a href="/app" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-12 py-6 rounded-2xl font-black text-xl hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all shadow-xl hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 relative z-10">
						Start Creating with AI
					</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<footer class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8">
			<div class="text-xl font-black tracking-tighter text-blue-500">MORPHOS</div>
			<div class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">© 2024 Morphos AI. All rights reserved. Precise. Parametric. Production-ready.</div>
			<div class="flex gap-6 text-slate-400">
				<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Twitter</a>
				<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
